snippet.title: The Choreographist - Hollow Bodies - BOSS FIGHT
snippet.description:
The Choreographist is combat. It is music. It is... almost a thing that was.
Joined by her two handy cohorts, witness the battle... against Mrrgurina!

This is the Third Boss Fight of Story Mode.
Beat the boss before time runs out... Or Pizza.. will call out FOR YOU.

Music courtesy of J-Punch and Dave Moonshine. Because we gave them hugs and candy.

GET THE FULLY-PLAYABLE, INCOMPLETE THANG FREE RIGHT NOW:
https://akuparagames.itch.io/the-choreographist
